<p class="en">This diagnosis builds on earlier pieces covering the <a href="/en/blog/ssr-dry-powder-illusion">SSR dry-powder illusion check</a>, the <a href="/en/blog/stablecoin-cap-largest-drop-since-terra">stablecoin market cap's largest drop since Terra</a>, the <a href="/en/blog/mvrv-lth-sopr-value-zone-price-standoff">MVRV/LTH-SOPR value zone vs. the 307-day standoff</a>, and the <a href="/en/blog/sentiment-outpaces-leverage-whale-deposit-gap">Fear &amp; Greed vs. leverage gap diagnosis</a>.</p>
<p class="ja">この診断は、先に取り上げた<a href="/ja/blog/ssr-dry-powder-illusion">SSRマル・パウダー錯視点検</a>、<a href="/ja/blog/stablecoin-cap-largest-drop-since-terra">テラ事態以降最大の下落幅を記録したステーブルコイン時価総額診断</a>、<a href="/ja/blog/mvrv-lth-sopr-value-zone-price-standoff">MVRV・LTH-SOPRバリューゾーンと307日価格の食い違い診断</a>、<a href="/ja/blog/sentiment-outpaces-leverage-whale-deposit-gap">恐怖強欲指数・レバレッジ乖離診断</a>の延長線上にある。</p>

<p class="es">Este diagnóstico se apoya en las piezas anteriores sobre la <a href="/es/blog/ssr-dry-powder-illusion">verificación de la ilusión de pólvora seca del SSR</a>, la <a href="/es/blog/stablecoin-cap-largest-drop-since-terra">mayor caída de la capitalización de stablecoins desde Terra</a>, el <a href="/es/blog/mvrv-lth-sopr-value-zone-price-standoff">diagnóstico de la zona de valor MVRV/LTH-SOPR frente al estancamiento de 307 días</a>, y el <a href="/es/blog/sentiment-outpaces-leverage-whale-deposit-gap">diagnóstico de la brecha entre Miedo y Codicia y el apalancamiento</a>.</p>
<p class="de">Diese Einordnung baut auf den früheren Beiträgen zur <a href="/de/blog/ssr-dry-powder-illusion">Überprüfung der SSR-Trockenpulver-Illusion</a>, zum <a href="/de/blog/stablecoin-cap-largest-drop-since-terra">größten Rückgang der Stablecoin-Marktkapitalisierung seit Terra</a>, zur <a href="/de/blog/mvrv-lth-sopr-value-zone-price-standoff">Einordnung der MVRV/LTH-SOPR-Wertzone gegen den 307-Tage-Stillstand</a> und zur <a href="/de/blog/sentiment-outpaces-leverage-whale-deposit-gap">Einordnung der Fear-&amp;-Greed-versus-Leverage-Lücke</a> auf.</p>
<p class="fr">Ce diagnostic s'appuie sur les articles précédents sur la <a href="/fr/blog/ssr-dry-powder-illusion">vérification de l'illusion de poudre sèche du SSR</a>, la <a href="/fr/blog/stablecoin-cap-largest-drop-since-terra">plus forte baisse de la capitalisation des stablecoins depuis Terra</a>, le <a href="/fr/blog/mvrv-lth-sopr-value-zone-price-standoff">diagnostic de la zone de valeur MVRV/LTH-SOPR face à l'impasse de 307 jours</a>, et le <a href="/fr/blog/sentiment-outpaces-leverage-whale-deposit-gap">diagnostic de l'écart entre Fear &amp; Greed et le levier</a>.</p>
<p class="pt">Este diagnóstico se apoia nas peças anteriores sobre a <a href="/pt/blog/ssr-dry-powder-illusion">verificação da ilusão de pólvora seca do SSR</a>, a <a href="/pt/blog/stablecoin-cap-largest-drop-since-terra">maior queda da capitalização de stablecoins desde a Terra</a>, o <a href="/pt/blog/mvrv-lth-sopr-value-zone-price-standoff">diagnóstico da zona de valor MVRV/LTH-SOPR contra o impasse de 307 dias</a>, e o <a href="/pt/blog/sentiment-outpaces-leverage-whale-deposit-gap">diagnóstico da lacuna entre Medo e Ganância e a alavancagem</a>.</p>
<p class="tr">Bu değerlendirme, daha önceki <a href="/tr/blog/ssr-dry-powder-illusion">SSR kuru barut yanılsaması kontrolüne</a>, <a href="/tr/blog/stablecoin-cap-largest-drop-since-terra">Terra'dan bu yana en büyük düşüşü kaydeden stablecoin piyasa değeri değerlendirmesine</a>, <a href="/tr/blog/mvrv-lth-sopr-value-zone-price-standoff">MVRV/LTH-SOPR değer bölgesi ile 307 günlük çıkmaz değerlendirmesine</a> ve <a href="/tr/blog/sentiment-outpaces-leverage-whale-deposit-gap">Korku ve Açgözlülük ile kaldıraç arasındaki fark değerlendirmesine</a> dayanıyor.</p>
<p class="vi">Phân tích này được xây dựng dựa trên các bài viết trước đó về <a href="/vi/blog/ssr-dry-powder-illusion">kiểm tra ảo giác thuốc súng khô SSR</a>, <a href="/vi/blog/stablecoin-cap-largest-drop-since-terra">mức giảm vốn hóa stablecoin lớn nhất kể từ Terra</a>, <a href="/vi/blog/mvrv-lth-sopr-value-zone-price-standoff">chẩn đoán vùng giá trị MVRV/LTH-SOPR đối đầu với bế tắc 307 ngày</a>, và <a href="/vi/blog/sentiment-outpaces-leverage-whale-deposit-gap">chẩn đoán khoảng cách giữa Sợ hãi &amp; Tham lam và đòn bẩy</a>.</p>

